originalText.text: I've been living here with my family for almost 2 years now and was amazed by the kindness of the staff. Maintenance is always up to date, building is clean, staff is welcoming, friendly and very helpful. I'm not sure why there is a review calling out two employees (Andy and Victor) as they are the kindest employees that work there. If anything...Andy, Victor and Kenny are the foundation of this building and would not be the same without them. They are all extremely hard working and truly care for me and my family. They are never lazy or rude to anyone, if anything they are always the three that are on top of things without any of us having to ask. My family and I are grateful to have them here.

originalText.text: Amazing building amazing front desk staff. However there are two morning guys that are extremely rude and lazy. One’s name is Andy(the package guy) and Victor(the door guy). The rest of the staff is great however, these two, I’m not quite sure how they got there jobs. But anyway my husband and I moved out due to COVID, great building overall, apart from those two.
